    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An old-school shooting gallery game for everyone</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041650/extras/fa1b2fe3c445d9808f626fea7be32d94.poster.avif?t=1735418838\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041650/extras/fa1b2fe3c445d9808f626fea7be32d94.webm?t=1735418838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041650/extras/fa1b2fe3c445d9808f626fea7be32d94.mp4?t=1735418838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Click or tap your way through <strong>cute, nature-themed dioramas</strong>.<br><br>Experience <strong>a variety of colorful worlds</strong> and <strong>minigames</strong>. Each of the eight worlds or minigames has three <strong>levels of increasing difficulty</strong> for a total of <strong>twenty four levels to master. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041650/extras/ea0ac310b41c8b16f754e345c70cd56a.poster.avif?t=1735418838\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041650/extras/ea0ac310b41c8b16f754e345c70cd56a.webm?t=1735418838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041650/extras/ea0ac310b41c8b16f754e345c70cd56a.mp4?t=1735418838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Two ways to play</h2><br><strong>School Mode:</strong> Play through the multiple levels in a row and try to earn a passing grade. Unlock new worlds and levels to play in the Arcade.<br><br><strong>Arcade Mode:</strong> Play individual levels and train your skills to earn an A+.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041650/extras/highscoresSS2_rounded.PNG?t=1735418838\" /></span>",
